        "data": {
          "label": "A Dictionary in Englyshe and Welshe: Where as emongeste other sondry & manifolde good and godlye ordinaunces bothe mooste wyselye inue_n_tede & mooste effectuously performede and put in use by your grace moste noble and Redoubtede Prynce, Whereby youre Royalmes and dominions haue receauede infinitte co_m_modyties and auoyde greate displeasures and disturbaunce whyche bothe nowe disquiet other Royalmes and before your graces tyme hath also uexed thys your Royalme of Englande [...]",
